reviewText: These episodes highlight Gods' love for us, our love for Him, and how we should love one another in a Godly way. While not a replacement for a Church Service-they can help teach to youngsters as well as non-believers what true Christianity is all about. Sometimes learning "by example" works best in a fictional story setting like these. Whether alone or with close family or friends you can allow your emotions to have free reign while viewing and not keep the worlds view of "manly" control of yourself.
summary: Brings a sense of peace to you.

reviewText: This dvd was good but I was hoping for the entire season to come out. I already have 3 of the 4 episodes and I was hoping to get some that I didn't already have.
I'm not good with words but this is wonderful.  Well worth the wait for this collection.  Thank you a lot.
Touched By an Angel is a Perfect Show for the family! I Always like how our Father God in Heaven is used in this Show!

This is a beautiful collection on true love and turning to God during trials and tribulations.The stories show that love conquers all and makes the heart warmer.You will need tissues for the heartfelt messages that you will hear.
This is a good show. Kind of disappointed that seasons 5 thru 9 aren't out yet, but these are good stories anyway. They always made you think. Maybe the rest of the seasons will come out later!!

This review is for the marketing and packaging only. Touched by an Angel is one of my favorite shows ever (along with 24.) CBS (or whoever) give us seasons 5 -9 instead of these best ofs. I urge consumers to not buy these packages and leave comments so that maybe the genius in charge of all this will get the message!
God's power, love and mercy. The season 1-4 include audio and subtitle in spanish, but this DVDs not include. I highly recommend it.
